# reftab — reference/table surface, results spec-sourced from the reference-types semantics
# (table instructions; a null-slot call_indirect → uninitialized element; table.grow returns old size).
invoke isnull i32:0 => return i32:0
invoke isnull i32:1 => return i32:1
invoke call0 i32:41 => return i32:42
invoke callnull i32:7 => trap uninitialized element
invoke isnull i32:100 => trap out of bounds table access
invoke size => return i32:3
invoke setcall i32:5 => return i32:6
invoke isnull i32:1 => return i32:0
invoke grow2 => return i32:3
invoke size => return i32:5
invoke isnull i32:3 => return i32:1
invoke fill1 => return i32:0
